FBIS3-24859 "drafr023bb_94003" FBIS-AFR-94-023 Document Type:Daily Report 3 February 1994 INTER-AFRICAN AFFAIRS OAU Ministers Continue Meeting in Addis Ababa 1-2 Feb Agree To Strengthen Conflict Resolution EA0202213594 Addis Ababa Voice of Ethiopia Network in Amharic 1700 GMT 2 Feb 94 EA0202213594 Addis Ababa Voice of Ethiopia Network Language: Amharic Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] The 59th OAU Council of Ministers meeting has agreed to strengthen the conflict prevention and resolution mechanism which was established in December 1993 by the OAU heads of state summit in Cairo. The meeting not only allocated 5 percent of the organization's regular budget to it, but also called on all member states to give additional assistance to enhance its functioning. It was also announced that a decision from the 35th country, enabling the establishment of an African economic community, has been received from Cameroon. [passage omitted]
